comments: Kleber (DAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Joseph's (SAC) path and does not deliver the contact.
Holmes (SAC) makes marginal contact with Doncic's (DAL) left arm/front at the end of the drive and does not affect his ability to pass.
Holmes (SAC) grabs and twists Kleber's (DAL) shorts during rebounding.
Finney-Smith (DAL) extends into Fox's (SAC) path and delivers contact to Fox's upper half that dislodges him from position.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) pulls up prior to Joseph (SAC) extending his left leg outward and initiating contact following the release of his jump shot attempt.
Fox (SAC) makes incidental contact with Finney-Smith's (DAL) right arm after making clean contact with the ball during rebounding.
Kleber (DAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Barnes' (SAC) path and does not deliver the contact. They each then engage and disengage with one another as they move toward the lane.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) retreats away from Fox (SAC) as he gathers the ball and Fox (SAC) jumps back into him on his driving shot attempt.
Kleber (DAL) makes incidental contact with Fox's (SAC) side as they each attempt to retrieve the rebound.
Fox (SAC) does not have full control or possession of the ball as he taps it off of the backboard during rebounding, at which point Kleber (DAL) makes legal contact with the ball.

Joseph (SAC) makes marginal contact with Doncic's (DAL) backside, then makes slight contact to Doncic's right arm, but Doncic is able to maintain full control of the ball. There is not clear and conclusive video evidence determining if Joseph makes any contact with Doncic's face.
Doncic (DAL) makes incidental contact with Fox's (SAC) lower half as Fox moves back into him during rebounding.
Bazemore (SAC) makes marginal contact to Wright's (DAL) side on his driving shot attempt.
Bjelica (SAC) makes marginal contact with Finney-Smith's (DAL) left forearm after the release of his put-back attempt and does not affect his ability to follow through naturally.
Bjelica (SAC) makes marginal contact to Finney-Smith's (DAL) side as he reaches for the rebound.
Bazemore (SAC) makes incidental contact with Kleber's (DAL) right arm during rebounding.
Bjelica (SAC) makes marginal contact to Doncic's (DAL) hand after the release of his shot and does not affect his ability to follow through naturally.
Joseph (SAC) makes marginal body contact with Doncic's (DAL) front/side after his gather.
Kleber (DAL) moves slightly forward and makes marginal body contact with Fox (SAC) prior to the start of Fox's upward shooting motion.
Kleber (DAL) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Fox (SAC) after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Doncic (DAL) makes marginal contact with his off-arm to Fox's (SAC) front as he changes direction and steps backward.
Bjelica (SAC) briefly has his hand on Kleber's (DAL) opposite hip before correcting.
Bjelica (SAC) steps forward and makes marginal contact with his left forearm to Doncic's (DAL) front.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) and Hield (SAC) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Kleber (DAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Giles III's (SAC) path and does not deliver the contact.
Joseph (SAC) makes marginal contact with Doncic's (DAL) lower half after his gather.
Hield (SAC) makes marginal contact with his extended left hand to Finney-Smith's (DAL) front as Finney-Smith retrieves the rebound and attempts the put-back.
Joseph (SAC) makes marginal contact with Burke's (DAL) side prior to the timeout being awarded.
Barnes (SAC) makes marginal contact with Finney-Smith's (DAL) front in the back-court.
Joseph (SAC) makes marginal contact with Doncic's (DAL) backside after he receives the pass in the front-court.
Kleber (DAL) is firming up in Joseph's (SAC) path and absorbs the contact during the screen.
Giles III (SAC) makes a slight brush to Doncic's (DAL) side during his drive to the basket.  The contact occurs prior to his gather.
Giles III (SAC) makes marginal contact with Doncic's (DAL) left hip after his gather.
Hield (SAC) commits the take foul on Hardaway Jr. (DAL).
Hield (SAC) wraps Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) upper half with both arms and affects his FOM during the inbound.
Barnes (SAC) commits the take foul on Finney-Smith (DAL).
Giles III (SAC) firms up in his screening position in Finney-Smith's (DAL) path and does not deliver the contact.
Giles III (SAC) extends and wraps his left arm around Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) right side, affecting Hardaway Jr.'s ability to defend.
Burke (DAL) and Barnes (SAC) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Fox (SAC) commits the take foul on Finney-Smith (DAL).
Hield (SAC) and Finney-Smith (DAL) come together and quickly separate during the inbound.
Burke (DAL) and Hield (SAC) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Hield (SAC) commits the take foul on Burke (DAL).
